Usage: specify_cell_virtual_align [-help] -cell <cells> [-mask <id>]
                                  [-pin_x_loc <microns>]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-cell <cells>                 # lib-cells with virtual alignment requirement
                              # ((libCell/ptnCell)+, required)
-mask <id>                    # virtual mask value for first track in cell
                              # (int, optional)
-pin_x_loc <microns>          # loc of the virtual geom from cell-boundary
                              # (default: first track loc) (float, optional)